    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076200/extras/88c3d6101a3b302b7c71b10e1b0e7fb6.poster.avif?t=1765350398\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076200/extras/88c3d6101a3b302b7c71b10e1b0e7fb6.webm?t=1765350398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076200/extras/88c3d6101a3b302b7c71b10e1b0e7fb6.mp4?t=1765350398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's the late 1990s. You follow Marcus as he returns to his hometown, Ashwood, for what he hopes will be the last time. He is there because of a mysterious letter he received just a few days earlier following his uncle's unexpected death. As Marcus learns more about what his uncle was doing before his death, the more he starts questioning the truth about the most significant tragedy in Ashwood's history.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ashwood Conspiracy is a story-rich point-and-click adventure game. There is a strong focus on the story, while puzzles are used to advance the narrative.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076200/extras/d7cc540ae202f632fd5b8622165e32dd.poster.avif?t=1765350398\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076200/extras/d7cc540ae202f632fd5b8622165e32dd.webm?t=1765350398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076200/extras/d7cc540ae202f632fd5b8622165e32dd.mp4?t=1765350398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>UNIQUE STORYLINE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story is set in Ashwood, a fictional city. Once the crown jewel of Karranthia, it has in recent years withered into a place of despair and slow decay. While on the surface it might seem like a traditional Rust Belt city, its dark corners hide many mysteries and secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features Slavic culture, traditions, and mythology.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076200/extras/29efb67b8f522e35f990230576f2d055.poster.avif?t=1765350398\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076200/extras/29efb67b8f522e35f990230576f2d055.webm?t=1765350398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076200/extras/29efb67b8f522e35f990230576f2d055.mp4?t=1765350398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EXPLORATION</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the unique and atmospheric scenes, all drawn by hand pixel by pixel. Explore abandoned factory buildings, descend into dark sewers, uncover hidden occult sanctums, and dig through secrets on 90s-era devices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076200/extras/e3ed0c8ac4e6746bea91fceda4cc0f85.poster.avif?t=1765350398\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076200/extras/e3ed0c8ac4e6746bea91fceda4cc0f85.webm?t=1765350398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076200/extras/e3ed0c8ac4e6746bea91fceda4cc0f85.mp4?t=1765350398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PUZZLES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Designed to challenge you and progress the story while still being fun and fair (no pixel hunting or moon logic).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076200/extras/24eb9b5d5e0b897b92f0ae5a428a47b5.poster.avif?t=1765350398\" width=800 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076200/extras/24eb9b5d5e0b897b92f0ae5a428a47b5.webm?t=1765350398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076200/extras/24eb9b5d5e0b897b92f0ae5a428a47b5.mp4?t=1765350398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>INVENTORY (PUZZLES)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you explore, you will discover items that will help you solve puzzles and overcome obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some items you can take a closer look at, while others you can combine to craft a unique item.</p>",
